G. Troy Meier 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Executive Officer at SUPERIOR DRILLING PRODUCTS, G. Troy Meier  made $638,454 in total compensation.  Of this total $443,942 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $175,750 was awarded as stock and $18,762 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2015 fiscal year. 


