  Superior Drilling Products, Inc. (SDPI) Files Form 4 Insider Buying : G. Troy Meier  Buys  5,000 Shares – Energy Index          Search       Superior Drilling Products, Inc. (SDPI) Files Form 4 Insider Buying : G. Troy Meier  Buys  5,000 Shares       Lauren Austin    June 8, 2017         Superior Drilling Products, Inc. (SDPI): G. Troy Meier , CEO of Superior Drilling Products, Inc.  purchased 5,000 shares on Jun 1, 2017. The Insider buying transaction was reported by the company on Jun 5, 2017 to the Securities and Exchange Commission. The shares were purchased at $0.80 per share for a total value of $3,995.00  , the company said in a SEC Form 4 Filing.Other Insider transactions have been reported by the company according to SEC Form 4, on May 30, 2017, G. Troy Meier  (CEO) purchased 2,097 shares at $0.88 per share price.On May 30, 2017, Annette Meier  (President) purchased 2,097 shares at $0.88 per share price.Superior Drilling Products: On Tuesday, May 30, 2017 heightened volatility was witnessed in Superior Drilling Products which led to swings in the share price. The shares opened for trading at $0.89 and hit $0.9 on the upside , eventually ending the session at $0.9, with a gain of 2.27% or 0.02 points. The heightened volatility saw the trading volume jump to 20,908 shares. The 52-week high of the share price is $2.72 and the company has a market cap of $22 M . The 52-week low of the share price is at $0.7225.     Lauren AustinTo contact the author of this report, send an email to lauren.austin@energyindexwatch.comYou might also likeBankfinancial Corp (BFIN) Files Form 4 Insider Selling : Paul A Cloutier  Sells  10,000 Shares Bankfinancial Corp (BFIN): Paul A Cloutier ,…Opko Health, Inc. (OPK) Files Form 4 Insider Buying : Gamma Investments Trust Frost  Buys  1,800 Shares Opko Health, Inc. (OPK): Gamma Investments Trust…Chesapeake Energy Corp (CHK) Files Form 4 Insider Buying : R Brad Martin  Buys  20,400 Shares Chesapeake Energy Corp (CHK): R Brad Martin…Le